        "short_description": {
            "neo4j_apollo": "CORP by AHK Tunisia is a department of the Chambre Tuniso-Allemande de l'Industrie et du Commerce, dedicated to improving youth employability in Tunisia. It connects job seekers, particularly students and graduates, with recruiters through various professional programs, career transitions, and employment events. With a focus on skill development and market insertion, CORP addresses unemployment by promoting professional reconversion into high-demand sectors and offering soft skills training.\n\nCelebrating a decade of impact, CORP runs initiatives like the Employ’Net project, which supports job seekers with comprehensive services, including job fairs featuring Tunisian and German companies. The organization also provides professional accompaniment through orientation sessions and career coaching, and it organizes job fairs to facilitate direct connections between candidates and employers. Additionally, CORP supports entrepreneurship by helping individuals develop and realize their business projects, ensuring that candidates are well-prepared for the evolving job market.",
